'''本·里維斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Benjamin Neil "Ben" Reeves'''}}；{{bd|1991年|11月19日}}）是一位在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]出生的[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是中場。現效力於[[英甲|英甲]]球隊[[吉林汉姆足球俱乐部|基寧咸]]。他也代表北愛爾蘭國家足球隊參賽<ref>{{cite web|title=Ben Reeves named in Northern Ireland squad for Cyprus friendly|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/26353415|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2014-10-15|date=2014-02-26|archive-date=2014-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140310173804/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/26353415|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Petrie|first1=Richard|title=Greece 0 Northern Ireland 2|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29506546|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2014-10-15|date=2014-10-14|archive-date=2015-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725052337/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29506546|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Greece 0 Northern Ireland 2, Euro 2016 qualifier: Kyle Lafferty and Jamie Ward maintain perfect start|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/euro-2016/11163275/Greece-0-Northern-Ireland-2-Euro-2016-qualifier-Kyle-Lafferty-and-Jamie-Ward-maintain-perfect-start.html#disqus_thread|accessdate=2014-10-15|work=Daily Telegraph|date=2014-10-14|archive-date=2015-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150603132234/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/euro-2016/11163275/Greece-0-Northern-Ireland-2-Euro-2016-qualifier-Kyle-Lafferty-and-Jamie-Ward-maintain-perfect-start.html#disqus_thread|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

